1. Fix your properties file since here `log4j.rootCategory=debug, console, file` you refer to `console` appender but here `log4j.appender.stdout=org.apache.log4j.ConsoleAppender` you define `stdout` appender. So that the line would look like `log4j.rootCategory=debug, stdout, file`
2. Make sure you import porper `Logger` class where you log your messages. Check that you are using `import org.apache.log4j.Logger;` but not `import java.util.logging.Logger;` or whatever else.
3. Make sure there are no other log4j configuration files in class path

